[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"New ideals\",\n    \"content\": \"<p>You have to be ideals of love and affection and not of domination and nonsense &ndash; all of you. You will be the first Sahaj Yogis. You are the one who are going to change the complete concept of life. The new ideals have to be established.<\/p>\"\n  }\n]